description:
Sponsored by American Express 

Tanya Thomas has made it her mission to help others feel confident in their skin — a passion that has defined her career in skincare. After years of training alongside dermatologists, she set out on her own, renting single rooms to treat clients one-on-one. As word spread, her waitlist grew to be as long as three months. In 2021, she officially opened the first Tanya Thomas Skin Clinic location in midtown Manhattan. 

Clients can expect to be treated like royalty — a mantra Tanya adopted after realizing genuine connection was missing from many of the clinics where she previously worked. From the moment guests walk into her clinic, they’re greeted with warmth and guided through personalized treatment plans designed for their unique skincare needs. Tanya and her team focus on results that last, ensuring every client leaves feeling their best and is equipped with the knowledge and products to maintain their progress at home.
